: rbind() cbind() 

#      
# Q_d = Q_s
# Q_d = 10 - 2P
# Q_s = -5 + 3P

#  3  Q_d, Q_s, P  
# Q_d - Q_s      = 0            ----------- (1)
# Q_d       + 2P = 10           ----------- (2)
#       Q_s - 3P = - 5          ------------(3)

#     rbind()     .
row1 <- c(1,-1,0)
row2 <- c(1,0,2)
row3 <- c(0,1,-3)
coef.mat <- rbind(row1, row2, row3)
coef.mat
##      [,1] [,2] [,3]
## row1    1   -1    0
## row2    1    0    2
## row3    0    1   -3
